txt.en: 'Now you will feel the anger of Lubach, heir of the great Golfimbul!'
'I'm Lubach! And I'm going to rule over these worms!'
'But... how can this be? I cannot be slain! I am... the heir... of...'
'What are you doing? Kill them all!'
'My new friend is no goblin, but he has sworn to uphold my glorious conquest!'
'I'm surprised you've made it here, but you won't leave here alive!'
'I have gained a powerful ally who will help me destroy this land!'
'Ã‰ogan will reward me well for your deaths! Attack!'
'You cannot hope to stand against my might! My new friend has sworn it!'
'Throw down your weapons! You cannot hope to stand against me!'
'My new friend told me you would try to fight, but it is all for nothing! You cannot win!'
'Will you look at this, lads? Another fortune-seeker! Finish this one too!'
'Deal with it the same way, boys!'
'Little chance this one's got as fine a prize as the other did, though. Pity.'
